data.description: Built in 2014, Open Concept mobile with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths on 3 lots in a quiet neighborhood with mature shade trees and a pool. Small area in back already fenced in for the pool and your small pets.  Lots of kitchen cabinets with an island open to the living room, and sliding glass doors to the backyard. Split master bedroom with a walk in closet and an additional linen closet in the Master bath.  Master bath also includes double sinks and an extra large shower.  Plenty of storage space in this mobile as well as a storage shed outside. POA offers park, boat dock and fishing pier.
